description: Updates a vehicle model (model manifest). If created vehicles are associated with a vehicle model, it can't be updated.

parameters.name: name
parameters.description: The name of the vehicle model to update.

parameters.name: nodesToAdd
parameters.description: A list of fullyQualifiedName of nodes, which are a general abstraction of signals, to add to the vehicle model. (string) ---

parameters.name: nodesToRemove
parameters.description: A list of fullyQualifiedName of nodes, which are a general abstraction of signals, to remove from the vehicle model. (string) ---

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the updated vehicle model.

nested_items.name: arn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the updated vehicle model.
